      <title>如何登录综合素质评价平台</title>
      <link href="/2025/02/09/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E7%B4%A0%E8%B4%A8%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0/"/>
      <url>/2025/02/09/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E7%B4%A0%E8%B4%A8%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="教程">教程</h2><h3 id="补充&lt;span-class=&quot;bd-box&quot;&gt;&lt;h-char class=&quot;bd bd-beg&quot;&gt;&lt;h-inner&gt;：&lt;/h-inner&gt;&lt;/h-char&gt;&lt;/span&gt;手机用户看这里">补充<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>：</h-inner></h-char></span>手机用户看这里</h3><p>在开始教程之前<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>我们需要先进入应用商店下载EDGE浏览器<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>打开进入第一步中的网站之后<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>。</h-inner></h-char></span></p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5CASUS%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20250209203717613.png" alt="image-20250209203717613"></p><p>点击下面<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-end"><h-inner>“</h-inner></h-char></span>…<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>”</h-inner></h-char></span>样式图标</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5CASUS%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20250209203832488.png" alt="image-20250209203832488"></p><p>再点击<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-end"><h-inner>“</h-inner></h-char></span>查看桌面网站<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>”</h-inner></h-char><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>再按照下述步骤进行即可</p><p><span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-end"><h-inner>（</h-inner></h-char></span>不一定要安装EDGE浏览器<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>但需要有<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-end"><h-inner>“</h-inner></h-char></span>查看桌面网站<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>”</h-inner></h-char></span>功能的浏览器<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>笔者懒得去找其他的浏览器<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>理论上chrome也是可以的<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>）</h-inner></h-char></span></p><h3 id="第一步-进入网站">第一步 进入网站</h3><p>网址<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>：</h-inner></h-char></span><a href="http://zhpj.hnedu.cn/login">http://zhpj.hnedu.cn/login</a><span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>先通过网址进入这个页面<img src="C:%5CUsers%5CASUS%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20250209201933114.png" alt="image-20250209201933114"></p><h3 id="第二步-找回账号">第二步 找回账号</h3><p>点击<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-end"><h-inner>“</h-inner></h-char></span>找回EEID账号或密码<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>”</h-inner></h-char></span></p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5CASUS%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20250209202205125.png" alt="image-20250209202205125"></p><p>点击<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-end"><h-inner>“</h-inner></h-char></span>找回EEID<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>”</h-inner></h-char></span></p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5CASUS%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20250209202236669.png" alt="image-20250209202236669"></p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5CASUS%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20250209202408940.png" alt="image-20250209202408940"></p><p>使用自己的身份证号找回EEID账号</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5CASUS%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20250209202520310.png" alt="image-20250209202520310"></p><p>复制好自己的EEID</p><h3 id="第三步-找回密码">第三步 找回密码</h3><p>点击<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-end"><h-inner>“</h-inner></h-char></span>立即登录后<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>”</h-inner></h-char><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>跳转到以下网址<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>：</h-inner></h-char></span><a href="https://sso.hnedu.cn/login">https://sso.hnedu.cn/login</a></p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5CASUS%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20250209202658594.png" alt="image-20250209202658594"></p><p>再次点击<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-end"><h-inner>“</h-inner></h-char></span>找回EEID或密码<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>”</h-inner></h-char><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>再点击找回密码</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5CASUS%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20250209202815870.png" alt="image-20250209202815870"></p><p>依照指引<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>完成找回密码的步骤<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-end"><h-inner>（</h-inner></h-char></span>记得准备身份证正面照片<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>找回密码需要用<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>）</h-inner></h-char></span></p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5CASUS%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20250209203020829.png" alt="image-20250209203020829"></p><h3 id="第四步-完成登录">第四步 完成登录</h3><p>回到网址<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>：</h-inner></h-char></span><a href="http://zhpj.hnedu.cn/login">http://zhpj.hnedu.cn/login</a></p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5CASUS%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20250209203216340.png" alt="image-20250209203216340"></p><p>完成登录即可</p><p><img src="C:%5CUsers%5CASUS%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20250209203341515.png" alt="image-20250209203341515"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
